svg.metadata: Created by FontForge 20141024 at Mon Jun 29 22:10:14 2015 By Jimmy Warting Maison Neue is the thoroughly reworked version of our early Maison typeface family. While the original version was constructed on geometric principles, Maison Neue has now been meticulously redrawn. Paying particular attention to harmony, rhythm and flow, the new typeface also accounts for up-to-date display and reproduction technologies to create a distinctly contemporary grotesque, with a classic touch and a friendly appearance. The whole family contains 12 styles thus far; each includes an extended Latin character set and a variety of OpenType features.
